    excerpt: 'Hacked email account? Act fast with these steps to regain control, secure your data, and prevent more damage.',
    category: 'safety-guides',
    tags: ['email', 'hacked', 'security', 'account', 'recovery', 'beginner'],
    readTime: '6 min',
